--[[
    Roblox Executable Script with Autoplay Bot Integration
    ----------------------------------------------------------------
    Features:
    - Auto-detects notes ("NoteTemplate") and matches them to Receptors (1-4 / X, C, N, M)
    - NEW: Multi-accuracy Modes (Perfect, Great, Good, Humanized Legit)
    - NEW: Anti-Miss Crossing Detection (solves skipped notes on fast scroll speeds)
    - Multi-note / Chord support (can hit multiple notes at the exact same time)
    - Object Recycling (Pooling) Support: Detects when notes are reset to the top and clears cache
    - Static Template Filtering: Automatically ignores hidden/inactive source templates
    - Dynamic Hold & Tap Support with overlapping hold safeguards
    - Safe-release safeguards to prevent stuck keys on toggle/close
    - High-precision coordinate detection using AbsolutePosition
    - Automated key presses via VirtualInputManager
    - Includes an On/Off Toggle and a Safe Close clean-up sequence
    - Draggable GUI Frame
--]]

